uster RCT design with ICC = 0.3. Individual and cluster-level power calculations with attrition adjustments.</div>\n        <a href=\"projects/stata3.qmd\" class=\"card-link\">View project вҶ’</a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"portfolio-card\">\n      <div class=\"card-bar bar-sky\"></div>\n      <div class=\"card-body-inner\">\n        <div class=\"card-tag\">Geospatial В· Fuzzy matching</div>\n        <div class=\"card-title\">Tanzania Ward Redistricting &amp; Causal Debiasing</div>\n        <div class=\"card-desc\">Reconciled 3,333вҶ’3,944 Tanzanian wards using ArcGIS shapefile overlap. Monte Carlo simulation proving collider bias persists at N=2,500.</div>\n        <a href=\"projects/stata8.qmd\" class=\"card-link\">View project вҶ’</a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"portfolio-card\">\n      <div class=\"card-bar bar-teal\"></div>\n      <div class=\"card-body-inner\">\n        <div class=\"card-tag\">Policy analysis В· Evaluation</div>\n        <div class=\"card-title\">Maternal Health Access вҖ” Rural Counties</div>\n        <div class=\"card-desc\">Designed and managed a multi-site program expanding prenatal and postpartum care for 42,000 residents across 11 counties. HHS-funded.</div>\n        <a href=\"projects/index.qmd\" class=\"card-link\">View project вҶ’</a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:1.5rem;\">\n    <a href=\"projects/index.qmd\" class=\"btn-outline-custom\">See all projects вҶ’</a>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<!-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ\n     LATEST WRITING\nв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ -->\n<div style=\"background:#F7FAFE;border-top:1px solid #D0DFF0;border-bottom:1px solid #D0DFF0;\">\n  <div class=\"content-section\">\n    <div class=\"section-divider\">Latest writing</div>\n    <div class=\"blog-list-card\">\n      <div class=\"blog-row\">\n        <div class=\"blog-date\">Apr 2026</div>\n        <div>\n          <div class=\"blog-tag\">Policy analysis</div>\n          <div class=\"blog-title\">Why most program evaluations fail before they start</div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"blog-row\">\n        <div class=\"blog-date\">Feb 2026</div>\n        <div>\n          <div class=\"blog-tag\">Data methods</div>\n          <div class=\"blog-title\">Using Stata simulate for rapid Monte Carlo power analysis</div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"blog-row\">\n        <div class=\"blog-date\">Jan 2026</div>\n        <div>\n          <div class=\"blog-tag\">Field notes</div>\n          <div class=\"blog-title\">What six months in a county health department taught me</div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:1rem;\">\n      <a href=\"blog/index.qmd\" class=\"btn-outline-custom\">All posts вҶ’</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<!-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ\n     AWARDS STRIP\nв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ -->\n<div class=\"content-section\">\n  <div class=\"section-divider\">Recognition</div>\n  <div class=\"trophy-shelf\">\n    <div class=\"trophy-card\">\n      <div class=\"trophy-star\">вҳ…</div>\n      <div class=\"trophy-name\">Engineering Excellence Award</div>\n      <div class=\"trophy-org\">Atlassian</div>\n      <div class=\"trophy-year\">2021</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"trophy-card\">\n      <div class=\"trophy-star\">вҳ…</div>\n      <div class=\"trophy-name\">Learning by Giving Foundation Grant Recipient</div>\n      <div class=\"trophy-org\">Center for Public and Nonprofit Leadership, Georgetown University</div>\n      <div class=\"trophy-year\">2024</div>\n    </div>\n       <div class=\"trophy-card\">\n      <div class=\"trophy-star\">вҳ…</div>\n      <div class=\"trophy-name\">Dean's Scholarship Award</div>\n      <div class=\"trophy-org\">Georgetown University</div>\n      <div class=\"trophy-year\">2025</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<!-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ\n     AFFILIATIONS\nв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ -->\n<div class=\"affil-bar\">\n  <span class=\"affil-label\">Worked with</span>\n  <span class=\"affil-chip\">Georgetown University</span>\n  <span class=\"affil-chip\">Walking Tree</span>\n  <span class=\"affil-chip\">Thelma Jones Breast Cancer Foundation</span>\n  <span class=\"affil-chip\">Atlassian Corporation</span>\n  <span class=\"affil-chip\">Apple</span>\n  <span class=\"affil-chip\">Zomato</span>\n</div>\n```\n"},"formats":{"html":{"identifier":{"display-name":"HTML","target-format":"html","base-format":"html"},"execute":{"fig-width":7,"fig-height":5,"fig-format":"retina","fig-dpi":96,"df-print":"default","error":false,"eval":true,"cache":null,"freeze":false,"echo":true,"output":true,"warning":true,"include":true,"keep-md":false,"keep-ipynb":false,"ipynb":null,"enabled":null,"daemon":null,"daemon-restart":false,"debug":false,"ipynb-filters":[],"ipynb-shell-interactivity":null,"plotly-connected":true,"engine":"markdown"},"render":{"keep-tex":false,"keep-typ":false,"keep-source":false,"keep-hidden":false,"prefer-html":false,"output-divs":true,"output-ext":"html","fig-align":"default","fig-pos":null,"fig-env":null,"code-fold":"none","code-overflow":"scroll","code-link":false,"code-line-numbers":false,"code-tools":false,"tbl-colwidths":"auto","merge-includes":true,"inline-includes":f